   President's & Secretary's Priorities

   Initiatives and priorities of President Bush and Secretary Paige
   include...
     * No Child Left Behind
     * Back to School, Moving Forward
     * White House Summit on Early Childhood Cognitive Development
     * Faith-Based and Community Initiatives
          + Rallying the Armies of Compassion
          + Unlevel Playing Field: Barriers to Participation by
            Faith-Based and Community Organizations in Federal Social
            Service Programs
     * New Freedom Initiative (Removing Barriers for Americans with
       Disabilities)
     * ED Management Improvement Team (MIT)
     * The President's Management Agenda (Fiscal Year 2002) PDF

      Archives of Information on Priorities of Previous Administrations

